parameters: Umi "Inside here... is the divine body of Meea?"
Luitesia "Yes... With this, I can regain my power and memories..."
Kru: "You froze all of a sudden, you scared me."
Luitesia: "No, I'm not sick. Both of you... don't you remember anything?"
Luitesia: "No... it's nothing... I was just a little... happy, that's all."

Luitesia: "Now... Kru. There exists a causality centered around you in
time."

Luitesia: "Because of that, you might have suffered... but maybe it was all
for this moment..."
Luitesia: "Now, I will consolidate all of your causality."

Luitesia: "All of time... the power of Kru from every world... gather
here..."
Kru: "This is... like the ghost I saw once..."

Luitesia: "All the emotions, all the curses, all the anger, all the
sadness..."

Luitesia: "To eradicate the root cause of all causality, lend us your
strength..."
Kru: "Yeah... hah hah... just a bit... shocked, that's all..."

Luitesia: "With this, Kru will no longer travel back in time. In other
words, this timeline will be our last challenge."
